{"tid":1425404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請留意，警察今晚的確係想扮好人，但完全失鳩敗左","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T01:15:09.000Z","uid":161430,"like":125,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0449edaf187707805bc1e8ec6ffad3a8af9b5eee","tid":1425404,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:05:49.000Z","msg":"除左有警察刻意對示威者講左句:  你地唔好咁嘈 會嘈到街坊 外<br />\n<br />\n最明顯 無可否認既位係佢地搵左警隊既傳媒聯絡員出場<br />\n着藍色背心呢種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.singpao.com.hk/image_upload/1483904489.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singpao.com.hk%2Fimage_upload%2F1483904489.jpg&h=be7e7b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知全晚最大既事就係佢地走去捉住左個區議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連埋今晚本身就係因為捉學生會會長而起<br />\n仲有白衫警打鳩藍衫警既事件<br />\n<br />\n反映到佢地內部都係做唔好個劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚行動完全失敗左喇 唔好意思"},{"pid":"c8159b63f37a4b4675617a3a4f16f32414306845","tid":1425404,"uid":161430,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"而好可惜<br />\n班傳媒聯絡隊，出場都未夠幾分鐘<br />\n警隊成個行動就突然又完左<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟你地專程call佢地出黎做乜?<br />\n你地比示威者睇到曬你地亂成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"0cf0647554435a49e333e8361dda294fe9461fe1","tid":1425404,"uid":27718,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:11:28.000Z","msg":"但有片段畀CCTVB用<br />\n<br />\n文宣：<br />\nPo IG<br />\nPo FB<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSEUawm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSEUawm.jpg&h=b373d22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTelegram(入到去記得要撳掣過bot check):<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=3868288d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a>"},{"pid":"a7ad0